videos.description: Washington RB Myles Gaskin runs 38 yards and manages to stay inbounds while stretching across the goal line for the score.
videos.headline: Gaskin stretches ball in front of pylon for TD

videos.description: Utah running back Zack Moss punches it in for a 4-yard score to tie the game up at 7-7.
videos.headline: Utah ties the game

videos.description: Utah DT Pita Tonga picks off Jake Browning and looks like he is going to return it to the house, but fumbles the ball out of bounds at the 11.
videos.headline: Utah's Tonga fumbles away would-be pick-6
